+
+// ── Export / Import ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
+//
+// We expose two endpoints that wrap the on-disk format gitnexus already uses:
+//
+//   GET  /export?repo=<name>&mode=index|bundle
+//        Streams a ZIP. mode=index packages just <repoPath>/.gitnexus/.
+//        mode=bundle packages the entire <repoPath> minus heavy junk
