+//        repoPath to match, and registers the repo by hitting /api/analyze
+//        on the gitnexus server (force=false → it reuses the existing index).
+//
+// We use the busybox zip/unzip binaries (added in Dockerfile.web) instead of
+// pulling a Node zip dep, because the docker-server runtime is dependency-free
+// today and we want to keep it that way.
