+    //   1. registerOnly=1 — write the registry entry directly. No /api/analyze
+    //      call, so the imported index isn't touched. The repo shows up in
+    //      the dropdown and its graph is browsable. Code Inspector will fail
+    //      gracefully when source isn't on disk.
+    //   2. default — call /api/analyze (force:false). Useful when the target
